{"tid":922682,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"留低Tg會有專人聯絡你 用英文書法寫張聖誕卡比你","createTime":"2018-11-30T14:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T12:22:50.000Z","uid":76829,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e04a6e3e6e0eaaf5bac9bdecd1bc88595fa5d98b","tid":922682,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"Hello <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人想收聖誕卡呢？<br />\n卡嘅款就係簡單平價款嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我會用英文書法寫（垃圾嘅我只寫到英文）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然除左Merry Christmas 大家都可以留低唔同嘅英文句子比我寫落你張卡到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫得樣衰嘅話，細細力插就得架啦<br />\n多謝咁多位巴打賞面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自貼兩款可選字形先 <br />\n(其實仲有兩款字形，可惜寫得唔靚，過唔到自己個關就唔貼啦，有興趣再擺上嚟啦）<br />\n<br />\n第一款：modern brush<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFuJdrp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFuJdrp.png&h=98ee8273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二款：copperplate <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKtByrq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKtByrq.png&h=d687e023&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dfd0e0c08bbae8eb2adbb4501c4a2636371ba95","tid":922682,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743744b166cc1f76aedc36964b2e978cb8b8fe06","tid":922682,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e2888994ffcf2cf17737dba7b62dc6d8aaad30","tid":922682,"uid":76829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":